WEBVTT

00:00:00.634 --> 00:00:03.666
Look at the hand, something very cool is coming.

00:00:03.666 --> 00:00:07.411
See how many people are getting this coolness on their hands.

00:00:07.411 --> 00:00:19.925
Modi, raise the hands. Those people in whose hands the cold has come, raise your hands.

00:00:19.925 --> 00:00:24.106
In the hand, those who have felt this cool-cool thing, raise your hands.

00:00:24.106 --> 00:00:31.582
So many people! Now, those people who have not yet received it, for them, we will do the hard work here.

00:00:31.582 --> 00:00:35.871
As for the speech, it is that I have become exhausted giving speeches.

00:00:35.871 --> 00:00:42.410
For information about Sahaja Yoga, you have the books.

00:00:42.410 --> 00:00:56.221
Please take them from here and read about it, and understand what Self-Realization is.

00:00:56.221 --> 00:01:03.181
This is a very subtle thing. Once it has happened, one must stabilize it.

00:01:03.181 --> 00:01:09.969
We have come as far as your Borivali. You also now please bring your presence to Bharatiya Vidya Bhavan on Monday.

00:01:09.969 --> 00:01:16.504
One has to do a little hard work to stabilize oneself. To get realization is easy.

00:01:16.504 --> 00:01:23.320
Even with music, a man gets realization. Now, what is this self Realisation? What are the benefits?

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:36.248
How should it be stabilized? For all these things, there is a center in your Borivali also, and here also—which day is the program, Modi?

00:01:36.248 --> 00:01:43.567
Yes, every Friday... where? Yes, Cooperative.

00:01:43.567 --> 00:01:53.262
Everyone has heard- In Swastik Cooperative Society, give them the address.

00:01:53.262 --> 00:01:58.225
Every Friday there is a program, you people go there.

00:01:58.225 --> 00:02:01.947
If you have any disease, that will also be cured. You will also get Self Realization.

00:02:01.947 --> 00:02:05.526
And those who are realized, it will be explained to them what this thing is.

00:02:05.526 --> 00:02:12.750
Many people think that once they have come to Mataji, the work is done, and after Self Realization." , they should just sit down. That is not the point.

00:02:12.750 --> 00:02:19.520
for self realization, you have to settle (jamna). This is a very subtle event happening inside us.

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:22.187
This is also a very heavy grace of the Almighty,

00:02:22.187 --> 00:02:24.130
because of which it happens.

00:02:24.130 --> 00:02:26.515
Ordinarily, this did not happen at all.

00:02:26.515 --> 00:02:30.754
But there is some miracle (karamat) in us, because of that it is happening.

00:02:30.754 --> 00:02:35.366
Yesterday I told you that among the powers within us,

00:02:35.366 --> 00:02:42.861
there is one power that connects us with the Almighty.

00:02:42.861 --> 00:02:51.856
The name of that power is Kundalini. She is in our spinal cord, in the triangular bone.

00:02:51.856 --> 00:02:58.614
She remains in a dormant state. When she sees that some 'Authority' (Adhikari) is standing before her..

00:02:58.614 --> 00:03:05.959
...then she stands up on her own. Just as we connect this rope or this connection to the 'mains'...

00:03:05.959 --> 00:03:12.608
...in the same way, that power joins us to that 'mains' and relates us to God.

00:03:12.608 --> 00:03:22.418
In this way, we know our Spirit (Atma). Spirit means we start seeing what faults are within us.

00:03:22.418 --> 00:03:29.008
Meaning, which defects are in our chakras and which defects are in the chakras of others.

00:03:29.008 --> 00:03:35.286
Through this, extreme peace descends within. Man’s life starts moving on a completely different level.

00:03:35.286 --> 00:03:39.246
This is what is to be gained by man; there is nothing else to be gained.

00:03:39.246 --> 00:03:43.597
In Sanskrit it was said.. Tvam ekam sharanyam, tvam ekam varenyam.'You are the only refuge, you are the only one to be chosen.'

00:03:43.597 --> 00:03:47.043
In the world, there is only the gaining of the Almighty through the Spirit.

00:03:47.043 --> 00:03:55.087
Nothing else is worth gaining. Once the nectar is gained, the joy starts coming.

00:03:55.087 --> 00:04:00.746
Then all things of the world seem to have no fun in them. But only then does a man become a 'human being'.

00:04:00.746 --> 00:04:04.665
And all his qualities become specially fragrant,

00:04:04.665 --> 00:04:09.438
and from that fragrance, the whole atmosphere becomes perfumed.

00:04:09.438 --> 00:04:15.215
And in that, it feels that 'until today, I did not know this life at all.' All these blossoms, we had never seen.

00:04:15.215 --> 00:04:20.627
This new life, we did not know. This thing is very necessary for everyone.

00:04:20.627 --> 00:04:26.136
Otherwise, the world cannot be saved. The whole world is sinking today, you know.

00:04:26.136 --> 00:04:33.642
There is only one way to save it: that man changes completely from within. And that happens only through Sahaja Yoga.

00:04:33.642 --> 00:04:40.633
Therefore, my request to you is that you do not have to spend any money for this. You do not have to take any trouble for this.

00:04:40.633 --> 00:04:49.223
Only to enter into Sahaja Yoga, you have to give a little time. Do not waste your time here and there.

00:04:49.223 --> 00:04:55.913
It is a very important thing because we are explaining to you, telling you, and giving Self Realization to you.

00:04:55.913 --> 00:04:59.395
We are working hard on you. We are removing your dilemmas and we are pulling out your diseases.

00:04:59.395 --> 00:05:05.528
In every way, a very heavy revolution—which should be called a Revolution—which has never happened until today, that is our idea to do.

00:05:05.528 --> 00:05:15.199
Because of which, a complete change comes within us. We become a very contented being and a peaceful Witness.

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:25.198
This is a great task. And to do this work, all you need is a little patience (sabur). With that patience, this work can happen.

00:05:25.198 --> 00:05:34.969
Through this, all the religious imaginations of the world, whatever superstitions are within us, all those wrong things we found—all those things drop away.

00:05:34.969 --> 00:05:45.983
Not only this, but the God about whom we have disbelief... and we think that our 'progress' (unnati) should happen...

00:05:45.983 --> 00:05:53.149
...but we only think of 'material' progress—that we should have ten cars, ten vehicles, etc.

00:05:53.149 --> 00:05:58.501
All those wrong things we think—we get freedom from all of them.

00:05:58.501 --> 00:06:02.853
Why? Who is it?

00:06:02.853 --> 00:06:20.053
We should be completely discharged from all these things. And that 'freedom' (chutti)... yes?

00:06:20.053 --> 00:06:27.910
This is all a tamasha (spectacle). What can be done? Women have a habit of making a spectacle.

00:06:27.910 --> 00:06:36.465
What kind of fit is it? It is a 'fit' of epilepsy.

00:06:36.465 --> 00:06:43.440
Take them out. They are making a useless spectacle. Who is here?

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:48.045
She has such a 'good' fit. It is epilepsy.

00:06:48.045 --> 00:07:01.139
What kind of fit is it? It is an obstruction (badha). For how many years? Then what is the need for her to come here? You are a very useless woman

00:07:01.139 --> 00:07:03.688
There is no need to bring all the sick. Come on, take her out.

00:07:03.688 --> 00:07:11.121
Then what is the need for her to come here? You are a very useless woman.

00:07:11.121 --> 00:07:13.898
Except for gathering all the sick, she has no other business.

00:07:13.898 --> 00:07:20.922
These are all signs of bhuts (ghosts). She has been getting fits for fifteen years. Bring her and sit her on Mataji’s head (khopri).

00:07:20.922 --> 00:07:25.597
Does anyone seek God, or are you just gathering all the sick of the world for me?

00:07:25.597 --> 00:07:33.074
These bhuts will come here only to harass everyone. These are all ghosts, symptoms of ghosts.

00:07:33.074 --> 00:07:35.519
They won't do their own good deeds; they will have to suffer the consequences.

00:07:35.519 --> 00:07:40.861
There should be some limit. Whenever you see a sick person, you pick them up and bring them.

00:07:40.861 --> 00:07:46.659
For fifteen years she is getting fits. Okay. Her treatment can happen.

00:07:46.659 --> 00:07:49.035
I have said a hundred times that there is no need to bring the sick.

00:07:49.035 --> 00:07:52.523
I will do the treatment. But they bring all the sick and keep them on my head.

00:07:52.523 --> 00:07:56.741
Now, what is the use even if we make them 'wrestlers' (pahlwans)?

00:07:56.741 --> 00:08:03.791
What will I do even after fixing their health? Tell me that. Why should God even fix them?

00:08:03.791 --> 00:08:08.938
He also has some thinking—to fix a man who will do His work.

00:08:08.938 --> 00:08:15.717
This is her constant habit. At least a hundred people this woman has brought like this.

00:08:15.717 --> 00:08:21.384
And I fixed all hundred people. Now she has brought another one. This is her habit.

00:08:21.384 --> 00:08:29.411
Come on, take them away now. A person who has been getting fits for fifteen years—if she gets a fit in front of me, what else will happen?

00:08:29.411 --> 00:08:33.644
Those who are possessed by bhuts, they only get ghosts on them with me. Coming here, they start shaking like this.

00:08:33.644 --> 00:08:37.526
Come on, let her get up. Let it be, let it be. Let her stay. Let it be.
Let her get well, then take her.

00:08:37.526 --> 00:08:43.749
This is all because of bhuts. This getting of fits—these are all symptoms of bhuts.

00:08:43.749 --> 00:08:49.646
So, let her be okay. What can she do about it?

00:08:49.646 --> 00:09:14.714
(speaking with sahaja yogis)

00:09:14.714 --> 00:09:20.644
Modi, Modi, you come... they bring all the trouble and put it on my head.

00:09:20.644 --> 00:09:23.939
You yourself think, why should we fix them?

00:09:23.939 --> 00:09:32.222
They have brought at least a hundred people to my head so far. A hundred people, this woman.

00:09:32.222 --> 00:09:37.291
And I fixed a hundred people and left them. But what has this woman done?

00:09:37.291 --> 00:09:46.684
Close the door. Close the door.

00:09:46.684 --> 00:09:53.219
And she always does the same kind of work. This is exactly the symptom of bhuts.

00:09:53.219 --> 00:10:12.149
Shall I close the door? Shall I close the door?
Close the door, son. Please close the door.

00:10:12.149 --> 00:10:21.792
I have said a hundred times, those who are attacked by bhuts, do not bring them here. This is the time for meditation (dhyan).

00:10:21.792 --> 00:10:24.316
Everyone has come here to meditate. They did not come to 'get Self Realization' such people.

00:10:24.316 --> 00:10:29.582
The kingdom of Satan moves in the world.

00:10:29.582 --> 00:11:11.106
(background chatter)

00:11:11.106 --> 00:11:19.323
A hundred people... and I told a hundred times that you should not bring anyone.

00:11:19.323 --> 00:11:43.126
(background chatter)

00:11:43.126 --> 00:11:45.531
Father’s debt (baap karza).

00:11:45.531 --> 00:11:55.505
There you saw—the saint is a saint. A saint should fix everyone. This is a 'good' account!

00:11:55.505 --> 00:12:02.612
A saint should eat everyone's shoes. He should be put on a cross. He should be killed.

00:12:02.612 --> 00:12:07.538
No matter how much we hit him, he should not say anything. 'Beware' of speaking!

00:12:07.538 --> 00:12:11.784
If anyone touches a saint, then see—I will fix them and keep them. Those days are gone.

00:12:11.784 --> 00:12:21.244
Give poison to the saints. Beat the saints, kill them, make their condition miserable. And the saint should not speak a single word!

00:12:21.244 --> 00:12:29.647
What is this? You have created a spectacle for me. Tell me, have you or haven't you? Now you tell me, how many of your people have I fixed?

00:12:29.647 --> 00:12:37.172
I have taken a contract for these people's fathers!

00:12:37.172 --> 00:12:43.238
Let her get up. She will be fine on her own.

00:12:43.238 --> 00:12:48.751
She will get up, she will get up. Leave her, leave her. She will get up by herself.

00:12:48.751 --> 00:12:52.935
She has been getting them for fifteen years—it is not a new thing.

00:12:52.935 --> 00:13:05.918
Let her get up.
Let it be, don't you worry about her.

00:13:05.918 --> 00:13:13.955
I say here a hundred times—do not bring bhuts-affected people. They come and start dancing like this in front of me.

00:13:13.955 --> 00:13:17.015
And then everyone goes and touches their feet like idiots.

00:13:17.015 --> 00:13:40.117
What? Who is talking? Come here and talk to me. What are you talking? Who is talking?

00:13:40.117 --> 00:13:52.270
Who is speaking here? If its heart attack I would have saved her.

00:13:52.270 --> 00:20:30.297
(music/bhajan) Today Mother has come to my house. O Mother, today you have come to my house.

00:20:30.297 --> 00:21:27.295
Today Mother has come, Power has come to my house,

00:21:27.295 --> 00:21:59.581
and I am full of joy (Anand).

00:21:59.581 --> 00:25:39.924
My heart and all my body, and mind, and all my money and property—everything I give.

00:25:39.924 --> 00:27:54.815
Victory to Immaculate Mother (Jai Nirmal Mata Di). Victory to Nirmal. Mother, give everyone Your blessings. Give everyone Your blessings.

00:27:54.815 --> 00:32:25.053
How many incarnations have You taken? O Mother, how many incarnations have You taken?

00:32:25.053 --> 00:32:55.834
Today Mother has come to my house. O Mother, today you have come to my house. Today Mother has come, Power has come to my house, and I am full of joy (Anand). My heart and all my body, and mind, and all my money and property—everything I give.

00:32:55.834 --> 00:37:59.391
One bhajan. One 'Hari Om'.
Hari Om. Hari Om.

00:37:59.391 --> 00:43:59.591
Sabko dua dena (Aarti)

00:43:59.591 --> 00:45:00.403
(Mahamantras)
